肤变化最难捉摸，她会因为肾上腺与甲状腺相对亢进，代谢加快，血液循环加速而变得红润，细腻。也会由于孕酮，睾酮较多，皮脂腺分泌旺盛导致面部油腻，粗糙，长东西。同样由于怀孕的关系，皮肤色素沉着加重，加之孕期女人需要格外小心护肤品中的化学成份，甚至孕中晚期开始不再护肤，最终皮肤通常会比之前糟糕。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;赞，乳房二次发育！&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;lin