kground-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	传统的月子只是产褥期的前30天，而整个产褥期通常需要6到8周时间，双月子就是由此而来。让身体恢复6到8周是必要的， 排出怀孕生产堆积的各种废物，让消耗了过多气血的身体恢复能量，是这个阶段的美丽目标。让细胞“吃饱”，才会有力气减肥与美容。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Ps：这里说一下产后卫生巾，一定要选好的，推荐舒珊卫生巾，有抑菌功能，所以对于顺产的人来说用舒珊伤口也好得快。舒珊还有暖宫的作用，可以促进气血循环，有助于排尽恶露。恶露排得干净不干净，对于产后恢复也是很关键的。这个时候，就别想着省钱了。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;化瘀，产后首要任务&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	尤其对于难产的女人，气衰血滞，代谢缓慢，延缓恢复进度。此时的目标应该是化瘀去水，提升代谢。在化瘀未完成前，不能进补。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;生产第一周要少喝水&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	饮食清淡为主，少盐油，有利于产后水分排出，如果自然排水效果不好，可以喝日本的甲等莫柔米，这是一种产自日本冲绳的天然活性酸，能疏通经络，改善代谢，产后喝还可以促进子宫收缩，促使恶露的排出，元气恢复。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	而且因为经络疏通了，气血就能顺畅，还能帮助产后乳汁的分泌，有的人因为产后气血耗损严重，经络堵，所以开奶困难，喝莫柔米是可以帮助的。坚持喝到哺乳期结束，身材恢复会更快。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;理气益血，补气血是女人一辈子要做的事，产后尤其重要&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	气血的补充不仅是身体的需要，也是美的开始，效果会直接反映在脸上。气血充足还能够加速产后恢复，也是产后减肥的重要基础，气血不足的女人是很难瘦的。平时多吃点补血的东西，五红粥，多喝五红水什么的，不过食补还是有限的，有条件还是直接喝铁元，铁元是德国的老牌补血产品，有几十年的历史了。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	铁元是全球50多国有售的，但是每个地区的配方不一样，记得要买中国版的，配方适合中国人，效果才好。生孩子是非常耗气血的，如果产后不及时把气血补回来，会留下后遗症。最好是一怀孕就喝铁元，不仅能改善因为孕期气血不足引起的失眠心慌，头晕乏力等症状，而且也不容易长色斑。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	我当时是一怀孕就开始喝铁元，喝到5个月的时候，手上的小太阳就长满了，脸上也没有长色斑，肤色红润有光泽，总是红扑扑的。喝莫柔米和铁元补气血，对于奶水的营养质量也很关键，奶水就是血养出来的。妈妈的气血一定要足，宝宝才可以从乳汁中获得全备的营养。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;会改变你体型的重要部分&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	怀孕生产导致骨盆宽大，耻骨联合分离等现象，会在分娩后2个月之内恢复。但如果恢复不到之前的状态，那么产后体型就会被固定下来。除了使用骨盆带之外，教一个自行调节的方法：\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	侧卧在硬板床上，如果是左侧卧，请将左手手心向下，放到胯骨之下，然后头脚抬起，全身重量通过胯骨这一个支点压到手上，而这样一个简单的动作，就可以有效的使骨盆的左右宽度，也就是耻骨联合分离的宽度减少，每次3分钟，每天2-3次，2-3周耻骨联合的分离就可以恢复到孕前状态。这一步，收窄你的骨盆，让你横向上小一号。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;一定要坚持使用腹带&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	爱美的女人产后一定要绑腹带，不仅能够帮助身材恢复，还能够预防内脏下垂与皮肤松弛，妊娠纹也会因为绑腹带得到改善。当然，要选择适合孕妇的腹带，它是一条长条状的带子，注意不要选择化纤材质。自然产建议产后第2天开始使用，剖腹产建议第6天开始使用。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;护肤品？缓一缓&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	月子中你气血充足的脸就是最佳风景，完全不必额外涂抹。但如果忍不住，婴儿护肤产品是你可以选择的。同时补充维C，维E及蛋白质食物会帮助你控制代谢废物转化成有色物质，减少黑色素产生。另一个好方法是养成定时大便的习惯，这将有利于肠道排毒，不至于被身体吸收使肤色灰暗，更恐怖黄褐斑，暗疮等。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote style=&quot;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;white-space:normal;margin:20px;padding:0px 20px;border-left-width:5px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#EAEEF1;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:25.1875px;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;padding:0px;line-height:1.8em;font-size:13px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#C0504D;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;关于月子的一些误区，不注意会影响下一阶段效果&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;骨头汤补钙，催奶&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	补钙方式尽量使用牛奶或者钙制剂。传统骨头汤钙含量并不高。用1公斤肉骨头煮汤2小时，汤中的钙含量也仅在20mg左右 ，并且由于骨髓的缘故，导致汤中脂肪含量很高，对恢复身材并不会有帮助。鱼汤可以喝，另外，汤并没有比肉更有营养！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/6H2fic5Al1elBGu97Kpbr79ib5c9sStYEfMpT7ebLPe2peM1zYQVN3sfnMSKf1AYI3PR9Ehaqn1ic2ldvSAib7vfKw/0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6581532416502947&quot; data_ue_src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/6H2fic5Al1elBGu97Kpbr79ib5c9sStYEfMpT7ebLPe2peM1zYQVN3sfnMSKf1AYI3PR9Ehaqn1ic2ldvSAib7vfKw/640&quot; data-w=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; _width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/6H2fic5Al1elBGu97Kpbr79ib5c9sStYEfMpT7ebLPe2peM1zYQVN3sfnMSKf1AYI3PR9Ehaqn1ic2ldvSAib7vfKw/640&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1.5em;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:16.3636360168457px;text-align:justify;border-left-color:#0070C0;border-left-width:10px;border-left-style:solid;padding:8px 20px;line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#0070C0;background-color:#EEECE1;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;拼命吃水果&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	水果本身是很好的恢复食物，但水果较多偏凉性，食用后可能导致恶露排出困难，并影响代谢，建议适量吃含铁丰富的水果，水蜜桃，香蕉，樱桃会比较适合。铁对于补血的帮助你不会不知道。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height: